# Xiaohongshu AI Agent v0.1.0

## 🎉 Foundation Release

We are excited to announce the first public release of Xiaohongshu AI Agent.

Xiaohongshu AI Agent is an open-source AI framework designed to help creators and developers build intelligent content workflows using Large Language Models.

---

## 🚀 Highlights

### AI Content Generation

- OpenAI-powered content creation
- Xiaohongshu optimized writing workflow
- Structured content output


### Prompt Engineering Framework

Introduced a modular prompt system:

- System prompts
- Agent prompts
- Templates
- Evaluation framework


### Open Source Ready

Added:

- MIT License
- Contribution guidelines
- Development roadmap
- Architecture documentation


---

## 🏗 Technical Foundation

Current architecture includes:

```
User

 ↓

AI Agent Workflow

 ↓

OpenAI Models

 ↓

Generated Content
```

