## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/meng6836355-oss/xiaohongshu-ai-agent.git

cd xiaohongshu-ai-agent

pip install -r requirements.txt
```

Configure:

```bash
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key
```

Run:

```bash
python main.py
```

